<section id="about-me" class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-photo-container">
                <dotlottie-player 
                    src="https://lottie.host/e9bb1186-c7f4-4181-8a73-bdff02f8440c/WCRkGPlthD.lottie" 
                    background="transparent" 
                    speed="1" 
                    loop 
                    autoplay>
                </dotlottie-player>
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dqbxkmkph/image/upload/v1759879976/ANaM_ynwj0v.png" alt="Ana Maria Posada">
            </div>
            <div class="text-left">
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Meet Ana Maria</h2>
            <div class="text-left  max-w-4xl">

    <p>
        <strong>Ana Maria</strong> is a <strong>multidisciplinary designer</strong> with the soul of a musician and the heart of an artist. Currently based in Vancouver, Canada, she originally hails from Colombia, where her artistic roots were nurtured. She holds a bachelor's degree in <strong>Social Communication and Journalism</strong>, a diploma in <strong>Digital Design </strong>, and has spent countless years immersed in <strong>music production and songwriting</strong>.</p>
            <br>
    <p>
        Her professional journey has led her to collaborate with a diverse range of clients, from independent entrepreneurs to creative agencies like <strong>Rethink</strong> as well as local icons like <strong>Science World</strong> and global brands such as <strong>IBM</strong> and <strong>Electronic Arts (EA)</strong>. As a <strong>Production Designer</strong>, her expertise spans across Web design, UI/UX, branding, and digital assets to animation, photography, and videography, often enhanced with the use of <strong>AI-powered tools</strong> to push creativity further.
        </p>
<br>
          <p>
        Driven by a passion for <strong>crafting visual content</strong> with meaningful impact, Ana is an <strong>eternally curious creator</strong> who blends creativity, technology, and strategy to design user experiences that are not only beautiful but also intuitive and human.
         </p>
</div>
